data.description: VETS - ASK ABOUT ASSUMING A 2.25% INTEREST RATE!  Located on a quiet Cul-de-sac this 4 beds, 2.5 baths, a 3 car garage with an additional storage room, plus a separate dining space, an office, and a living room area with lots of natural light is perfect for entertaining. there is a kids retreat upstairs. The home is also equipped with solar panels, a large backyard, and a deck/pergola combo so you can entertain guests outdoors without having to worry about crowding up your indoor space. If you're looking for something in Johnson Ranch that can accommodate large groups for parties or just want a place where people can come over for dinner without feeling like they're taking up space in your house, this is it!
